<h1>About AAACT</h1>

<p>This is the starter About page for the Digital Accessibility and Inclusive Design team.</p>

<h2>Our Mission</h2>

<p>To advance digital accessibility excellence and foster inclusive design practices across all our initiatives.</p>

<h2>Our Approach</h2>

<p>We believe that accessible design benefits everyone. By following Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) and best practices, we create digital experiences that are:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Perceivable:</strong> Information is presented in ways all users can recognize</li>
  <li><strong>Operable:</strong> Interfaces work with keyboard and other input methods</li>
  <li><strong>Understandable:</strong> Content and interaction are clear and predictable</li>
  <li><strong>Robust:</strong> Code is compatible with current and future technologies</li>
</ul>

